data.text:
Covid-19 update: Fulfillment time for orders to the UK and EU have not been affected, however delays may occur given the uncertainty of the situation. For orders fulfilled in the US, to ensure the safety of our colleagues, the fulfillment time (i.e. until the order gets dispatched) of fine art prints may take up to 3 weeks.

To minimise our carbon footprint and cut down on waste, all of our products are made to order.

It arrives in 1-2 weeks carefully wrapped in tissue paper in an industry-standard postal cardboard tube.

All orders to the UK, US and the EU are free of customs charges.

We ship internationally from fulfilment centres in the EU, the US and Mexico (Find out more).

We collaborate with trusted local carriers for reliable, on-time delivery and all of our shipping methods have tracking enabled.

Secure Payments

We are PCI compliant so that you can shop with confidence on USEUM Store and all sensitive customer information is fully encrypted using secure socket layer (SSL) technology.

Free Returns

If for any reason you are not entirely happy with your purchase, we will do our best to make it right. Please contact us within 30 days from the day you receive it, to ship a replacement, or to arrange a return for a full refund.
